oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Three female students posing near a car with Kirksey Old Main in the background. Written on the back: "Co-ed 1920 variety."

Prefatory statement from Coed Code, 1967-68: A Middle Tennessee State University student is expected under all circumstances to show respect for order, morality, and the rights of others, and to exhibit in her daily living a high sense of personal honor and integrity.
